longBusinessSummary: Tsutsumi Jewelry Co.,Ltd. engages in the manufacture, wholesaling, and retailing jewelry primarily in Japan. The company offers rings, earrings, necklace, pendent necklace, bridal jewelry, bracelet, and other accessories. It also offers jewelry design, as well as reconditioning and repair of pre-owned jewelry. In addition, the company operates precious stone trading centers in the United States, Belgium, Israel, India, and Thailand; and jewelry retail stores. It offers its products under Pure Planets, Blessed Rain, Classical Autumn, Modern Muse, Authentic Wedding, and TODAY's DIAMONDS brand name. The company was formerly known as Tsutsumi Precious Metals and Crafts Co., Ltd. and changed its name to Tsutsumi Jewelry Co., Ltd. in April 1988. Tsutsumi Jewelry Co.,Ltd. was founded in 1962 and is headquartered in Warabi, Japan.
